abstract: YONKERS, March 7--Mr. and Mrs. E. Prescott Barker of Yonkers and East Orleans, Mass., have announced the engagement of their daughter, Miss Barbara Barker, to Robert Allan Gibson, son of Mr. and Mrs. James O. Gibson of East Orleans.
